{"tid":1158533,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無熄咪密斟對話曝光 主席廖長江：流會無所謂 但西環實「拆天」","createTime":"2019-05-17T04:53:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-17T05:25:26.000Z","uid":86272,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5a4f5c5ad968ca9a8ffe15d31b46e9cc1e17f1f5","tid":1158533,"uid":86272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T04:53:02.000Z","msg":"立法會《國歌法條例草案》委員會今早開會，人民力量陳志全等民主派議員不滿建制派臨時加開會議，令三個委員會會議同時召開，分別在各會議上要求點算法定人數。惟在《國歌法》委員會點算人數期間，<span style=\"color: red;\">委員會主席廖長江未及「熄咪」，與副主席張國鈞對話密斟時，稱不介意《國歌法》委員會流會，但「西環實係（會）『拆天』。」</span><br />\n<br />\n根據基本法第二十二條 <br />\n中央人民政府所屬各部門、各省、自治區、直轄市均不得干預香港特別行政區根據本法自行管理的事務。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />捉到你了<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%9C%8B%E6%AD%8C%E6%B3%95%E5%A7%94%E5%93%A1%E6%9C%83-%E7%84%A1%E7%86%84%E5%92%AA%E5%AF%86%E6%96%9F%E5%B0%8D%E8%A9%B1%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89-%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD%E5%BB%96%E9%95%B7%E6%B1%9F-%E6%B5%81%E6%9C%83%E7%84%A1%E6%89%80%E8%AC%82-%E4%BD%86%E8%A5%BF%E7%92%B0%E5%AF%A6-%E6%8B%86%E5%A4%A9/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25AD%258C%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25A7%2594%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%259C%2583-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%2586%2584%25E5%2592%25AA%25E5%25AF%2586%25E6%2596%259F%25E5%25B0%258D%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E6%259B%259D%25E5%2585%2589-%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%25B8%25AD%25E5%25BB%2596%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%25B1%259F-%25E6%25B5%2581%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%2589%2580%25E8%25AC%2582-%25E4%25BD%2586%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E7%2592%25B0%25E5%25AF%25A6-%25E6%258B%2586%25E5%25A4%25A9%2F&d=2bx9SR3QHfMC8bM4fPAEXxyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=fa29afa6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25AD%258C%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25A7%2594%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%259C%2583-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%2586%2584%25E5%2592%25AA%25E